      RowBox[{"\[CenterDot]", "D"}]}], ")"}], "2"], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"462203a3-10e7-47e1-9dac-eb57e437e7ac"],
 ". When written in terms of derivatives with respect to P, H, V variables, \
it has to be a differential operator of order 6. We therefore write down the \
most general Ansatz:"
}], "Text",
