  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["s", "1"], " ", "=", " ", "1"}], ","}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "ee9004a7-a238-405d-9c5b-75f9ea4663e3"],
 " but this is not an allowed value for the spin of a doubly conserved \
operator. We can therefore choose it to be zero. Besides, if you would apply \
the constraint to ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["s", "1"], " ", "=", " ", "1"}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"171066ff-a7a5-471e-8320-da896606ab67"],
 ", you would find a(2) = 0."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9876462731256933`*^9, 3.987646417341364*^9}, {
  3.987646475998906*^9, 3.987646555612495*^9}, {3.987646789982491*^9, 
